      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
          Soft Normalized Advantage Functions for Reinforcement Learning in Optimal Control Problems
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
          <strong>Dilli Bhaskar</strong>, Athira Mullachery, Shaikshavali Chitraganti
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm italic text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">
          Accepted to 11th Indian Control Conference (ICC), Bangalore, 2025
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pub 2: Value-Based RL -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
        <img src="/assets/images/research/value_based_rl.png" alt="Value-Based RL" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
          Value-Based Reinforcement Learning for Mapless Navigation of a Mobile Robot
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
          <strong>Dilli Bhaskar</strong>, Ayyappadas Rajagopal, Nandagopan Kalathil, Shaikshavali Chitraganti
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm italic text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">
          Accepted to 11th Indian Control Conference (ICC), Bangalore, 2025
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2 text-xs">
          <a href="https://youtu.be/7Rbjgge6bqM" target="_blank" class="px-2 py-1 text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 rounded hover:bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/50">Video</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pub 3: Congestion-aware -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
        <img src="/assets/images/research/congestion_paper.png" alt="Congestion-aware Path Planning" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
          Congestion-aware Path Planning for Multiple Shelf Carrying Mobile Robots in RMFS
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
          <strong>Dilli Bhaskar</strong>, Selva Kumar Chandrasekar, Subramanian Saravana Perumaal
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm italic text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">
          Industry 4.0 and Advanced Manufacturing, Volume 1, Springer, 2024
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2 text-xs">
          <a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-981-97-7150-9_26" target="_blank" class="px-2 py-1 text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 rounded hover:bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/50">Paper</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pub 4: Thermal Fire -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
        <img src="/assets/images/research/forest_fire.gif" alt="Forest Fire Detection" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
          Early Thermal Forest Fire Detection using UAV and Saliency Map
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">
          <strong>Dilli Bhaskar</strong>, Suguna M.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm italic text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">
          5th International Conference on Contemporary Computing and Informatics (IC3I), 2022
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-2 text-xs">
          <a href="https://doi.org/10.1109/IC3I56241.2022.10072674" target="_blank" class="px-2 py-1 text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 rounded hover:bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/50">Paper</a>
